NK041(di)004:1: // dkyil 'khor spyi'i thig tshon gyi bya ba rab gsal kun dga' bzhugs so //
NK041(di)004:2: na mahsh+r+ai badz+ra sa t+wa ya /
NK041(di)004:3: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor kun gyi 'byung gnas che //
NK041(di)004:4: rje btsun bla ma'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal nas //
NK041(di)004:5: blo dman don du dkyil 'khor thig tshon gyi //
NK041(di)004:6: cho ga'i bya ba rab gsal kun dga' bshad //
NK041(di)004:7: re zhig thig la rnam pa gnyis //
NK041(di)004:8: ye thig dang ni las thig go //
NK041(di)004:9: ye thig skud rgyu pad+ma yi //
NK041(di)004:10: rgyus pa'am ras bal la'ang rung //
NK041(di)004:11: rgyu de dpa' bo'i rin gyis nyos //
NK041(di)004:12: bcu drug lo lon mtshan ldan mas //
NK041(di)004:13: bkal ba'i srad bu kha dog ni //
NK041(di)004:14: lnga'am yang na nyid shu lnga //
NK041(di)004:15: ring thung dkyil 'khor nyis bldabs la //
NK041(di)004:16: sbom phra sgo yi nyi shu cha //
NK041(di)004:17: ye shes lnga ru byin brlabs te //
NK041(di)004:18: gdab tshul slob dpon nub tu 'dug /
NK041(di)004:19: slob bu shar du gnas pa yis //
NK041(di)004:20: tshangs thig dang po mkha' la gdab //
NK041(di)004:21: de bzhin slob dpon lho dang ni //
NK041(di)004:22: slob rgyab 'gros ma byang 'dug gnyis pa gdab //
NK041(di)004:23: slob dpon me yi mtshams su 'dug /
NK041(di)004:26: shar gyi logs thig gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:29: srin por 'dug pas nub phyogs gdab //
NK041(di)004:30: slob dpon de nyid slob ma rgyab 'gros ni //
NK041(di)004:31: byang shar 'dug pas byang phyogs gdab //
NK041(di)004:32: slob dpon me dang slob ma rgyab 'gros ni //
NK041(di)004:33: srin por 'dug pas lho phyogs gdab //
NK041(di)004:34: slob dpon de nyid slob ma ni //
NK041(di)004:35: rlung nub byang gnas zur thig dang po gdab //
NK041(di)004:36: slob dpon srin po slob ma ni //
NK041(di)004:37: byang shar 'dug pas gnyis pa ste //
NK041(di)004:38: kun la g.yas skor khyad par du //
NK041(di)004:39: tshangs logs rgyab 'gros tshul gyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:40: gnam thig gdab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK041(di)004:41: de nas las thig rim pa bshad //
NK041(di)004:42: ras bal las grub srad bu ni //
NK041(di)004:43: kha dog gsum mam dgu sgril te //
NK041(di)004:44: ring thung sbom phra 'khol mkhan rin //
NK041(di)004:45: sngar bzhin byas pa'i thig skud de //
NK041(di)004:46: sku gsung thugs su byin brlabs nas //
NK041(di)004:47: thig brgyad go rim snga ma ltar //
NK041(di)004:48: 'debs sam yang na logs thig bzhi'i //
NK041(di)004:49: sngon du zur thig gnyis btab kyang //
NK041(di)004:50: gnas skabs bya sla 'gal ba'ang med //
NK041(di)004:51: 'debs dus slob dpon slob ma yi //
NK041(di)004:52: 'dug phyogs ye thig bzhin du gces //
NK041(di)004:53: de yang cung zad phye ste bshad //
NK041(di)004:54: khru gang tshad las mi chung ba'i //
NK041(di)004:55: ji ltar rigs pa'i gzhi'i ngos su //
NK041(di)004:56: dang po shar nub tshangs thig gdab //
NK041(di)004:57: de yi dbus su mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:58: de ni dkyil 'khor dbus yin no //
NK041(di)004:59: dbus nas shar nub tshad mnyam pa'i //
NK041(di)004:60: mtshan ma byas pa brkyangs pa yis //
NK041(di)004:61: lho byang gnyis su bya rjes bya //
NK041(di)004:62: de steng tshangs thig gnyis pa gdab //
NK041(di)004:63: de bzhin lho byang tshangs thig la'ang //
NK041(di)004:64: shar nub lta bu'i mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:65: de yi bar brkyangs srad bu ni //
NK041(di)004:66: phyogs bzhi'i mtshan ma'i steng bzung nas //
NK041(di)004:67: zur bzhir bya rjes mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:68: de steng zur thig gnyis po gdab //
NK041(di)004:69: ngos rer ji ltar 'tshams pa yi //
NK041(di)004:70: logs thig bzhi btab mda' yab thig /
NK041(di)004:71: mda' thig nas ni lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:72: zur thig bzhi po cha gsum bgo //
NK041(di)004:73: sum cha phyi ma'i steng bzung nas //
NK041(di)004:74: logs thig bzhi btab rtsa ba'i thig /
NK041(di)004:75: mda' thig dang ni rtsa thig bar //
NK041(di)004:76: phyed bgos cha chen gnyis 'byung ngo //
NK041(di)004:77: nang ma dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:79: cha chen phyi ma phyed bgos la //
NK041(di)004:80: phyi ma de yang phyed du bcad //
NK041(di)004:81: d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab 'byung //
NK041(di)004:82: de rjes nang gi rtsa thig nas //
NK041(di)004:83: rta bab phyi thig bar du ni //
NK041(di)004:84: tshangs pa'i thig gi g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)004:85: cha chen gnyis gnyis gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:86: nang ma phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK041(di)004:87: phyi ma cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK041(di)004:88: sgo khyud sgo 'gram sgo log dang //
NK041(di)004:89: mun pa ka ba ka rgyan 'byung //
NK041(di)004:90: rta bab brgyad ma la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:91: ka rgyan mtha' ru cha phran bsnan //
NK041(di)004:92: mda' yab phyi rol rta bab bya //
NK041(di)004:93: de la snam phran bcad lugs gsum //
NK041(di)004:94: brgyad ma bzhi ma bcu gcig ma //
NK041(di)004:95: phyi ma'i phyag len snga 'gyur gyi //
NK041(di)004:97: dang po snam bu brgyad ma ni //
NK041(di)004:98: mda' phyir cha chen gsum bcad pa'i //
NK041(di)004:99: nang ma gnyis po bzhi bzhir bgo //
NK041(di)004:100: rta bab snam bu brgyad yin no //
NK041(di)004:101: phyi ma dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:103: de dag phyi mtha'i rim pa ni //
NK041(di)004:104: rta rkang ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam //
NK041(di)004:105: chu skyes dang ni sgrom bu gnyis //
NK041(di)004:106: de las cha phran gcig gis ring //
NK041(di)004:107: zar tshag de las gnyis kyis thung //
NK041(di)004:108: sna 'phyang de las gcig gis ring //
NK041(di)004:109: chun 'phyang de las gnyis kyis thung //
NK041(di)004:110: shar bu de las gcig gis ring //
NK041(di)004:111: de las khyung mgo gcig 'phyar ro //
NK041(di)004:113: rgya tshad cha phran gnyis re ste //
NK041(di)004:114: pad+ma'i g.yas g.yon cha phran phyed //
NK041(di)004:115: dor sar ri dwags re re bri //
NK041(di)004:116: glang rgyab mig gsum bskor tshul ni //
NK041(di)004:117: snam rta bab kyi bu gsum pa'i phyi thig dang //
NK041(di)004:118: tshangs thig 'dzom pa nas bzung ste //
NK041(di)004:119: cha phran gnyis kyi dbus ma bskor //
NK041(di)004:120: mun pa pa ti'i phyi thig dang //
NK041(di)004:121: tshangs thig 'dzom pa'i g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)004:122: cha phran gnyis re phyin pa nas //
NK041(di)004:123: cha phran gnyis kyi g.yas g.yon bskor //
NK041(di)004:124: de rnams phyi ru cha re bskor //
NK041(di)004:126: snam bu dang po phyed dang bzhi //
NK041(di)004:127: gnyis pa gsum pa drug drug go //
NK041(di)004:128: bzhi pa la ni bzhi bzhi ste //
NK041(di)004:129: snam bu lnga pa cha phran gsum //
NK041(di)004:130: drug pa de nas tshangs rtser slebs //
NK041(di)004:131: de rnams phyi ru phyed re bcad //
NK041(di)004:133: mda' thig zur nas cha chen phyed //
NK041(di)004:134: dor ba'i zlum bskor nang du yang //
NK041(di)004:135: cha phran bskor ba rtsibs rten yin //
NK041(di)004:136: rtsa thig dang ni sgo khyud thig /
NK041(di)004:137: 'dzom pa nas bzung rtsibs rten la //
NK041(di)004:138: rtse reg g.yas nas g.yon pa dang //
NK041(di)004:139: g.yon nas g.yas par bskor bar bya //
NK041(di)004:140: 'di ni rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa'i lugs //
NK041(di)004:141: gzhan du sna tshogs rdo rjer bzhed //
NK041(di)004:142: de yi g.yas g.yon rwa skor tshul //
NK041(di)004:143: rta bab kyi snam bu gsum pa'i phyi thig dang //
NK041(di)004:144: tshangs thig 'dzom pa'i phyir rol du cha phran gnyis re phyin te 'dzom pa nas //
NK041(di)004:145: bzung ste ka rgyan rtse nas bskor //
NK041(di)004:146: de nas 'phred du cha phran gnyis phyi ru gcig /
NK041(di)004:147: phyin te snga ma'i tshad des bskor //
NK041(di)004:148: dbus rwa rtsa ba'i rgya tshad du //
NK041(di)004:149: cha chen gcig yin mi mthong yang //
NK041(di)004:150: rim phra rtse mo cha phran gnyis //
NK041(di)004:152: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i khor yug ni //
NK041(di)004:153: rtsibs rten phyi ru cha chen gnyis //
NK041(di)004:154: bskor ba'i nang ma phyed gtub bskor //
NK041(di)004:155: nang nas pad rdor me ri'i sa //
NK041(di)004:156: lte ba'i lha gnas skor tshul ni //
NK041(di)004:157: rtsa thig nang du cha chen re //
NK041(di)004:158: dor ba gru chad thig tu 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:159: de yi phyi rol cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)004:160: btab pa glo 'bur bzhi yi thig /
NK041(di)004:161: rgyar ni cha chen re re'o //
NK041(di)004:162: dkyil 'khor dbus nas gru thig bar //
NK041(di)004:163: tshad mnyam zlum skor gnyis skor ba'i //
NK041(di)004:164: gnyis ka'i nang du cha phran re //
NK041(di)004:165: bskor bas nang nas rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:166: lte ba mu khyud rtsibs bzhi dang //
NK041(di)004:167: phyi yi mu khyud sa yin te //
NK041(di)004:168: de rnams zhi ba 'bring po'i thig /
NK041(di)004:169: sgyu 'phrul khro dkyil lta bu yi //
NK041(di)004:170: sgo sbrags nang ma'i gdab tshul bshad //
NK041(di)004:171: sngar gyi gru chad thig de ni //
NK041(di)004:172: dkyil 'khor nang ma'i mda' thig yin //
NK041(di)004:173: mda' thig de nas lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:174: logs thig bzhi pos phyed mar bcad //
NK041(di)004:175: phyi ma cha gsum bgos pa yi //
NK041(di)004:176: nang ma'i nang du bzhi cha gdab //
NK041(di)004:177: glo 'bur lhag ma yul ma'i khyams //
NK041(di)004:178: bar ma dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:180: phyi ma phyed gdab phyi phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:181: d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab bo //
NK041(di)004:182: sgo ni rtsig pa'i nang thig nas //
NK041(di)004:183: mda' yab phyi thig bar du ni //
NK041(di)004:184: tshangs pa'i thig gi g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)004:185: cha chen re btab phyi phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:186: de mthar cha phran re re bgo //
NK041(di)004:188: logs thig bzhis bcad phyed nang mar //
NK041(di)004:189: dbus kyi zlum bskor zhi ba ltar //
NK041(di)004:190: bskor zhing phyi rol khor yug gi //
NK041(di)004:191: pad ra dang ni rdo re'i bar //
NK041(di)004:192: cha chen gcig bsnan dur khrod sa //
NK041(di)004:193: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i thig rim ste //
NK041(di)004:194: sgo sbrags gnyis ma gsum ma sogs //
NK041(di)004:195: kun la de bzhin sbyar te dpyad //
NK041(di)004:197: sgo sbrags shin tu mang po la //
NK041(di)004:198: phyi dkyil cha chen nang dkyil gyi //
NK041(di)004:199: tshad du byas nas nang ma rnams //
NK041(di)004:200: shin tu phra bas bya dkar 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:201: de nas tshogs chen 'dus pa yi //
NK041(di)004:202: thig gi gdab tshul mdo tsam bshad //
NK041(di)004:203: 'di la steng khang zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)004:205: nyis thog tshul du gnas pa ste //
NK041(di)004:206: steng khang zhi dkyil sngar bshad pa'i //
NK041(di)004:209: tshangs zur spyi ltar btab pa'i rjes //
NK041(di)004:210: ji ltar rigs pa'i mda' thig gdab //
NK041(di)004:211: mda' thig de nas lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:212: dum bu cha mnyam gsum du bgo //
NK041(di)004:213: sum cha nang ma'i steng bzung nas //
NK041(di)004:214: logs bzhi bcad pa gru chad thig /
NK041(di)004:215: gru chad thig nas mda' thig bar //
NK041(di)004:216: cha mnyam lngar bgos nang ma bzhin //
NK041(di)004:217: phyed phyed gtub pas dum bu dgu //
NK041(di)004:218: de ltar dum bu dgu po yang //
NK041(di)004:219: rang rang so so'i chags tshad kyis //
NK041(di)004:220: dum bu gsum gsum dag tu bgo //
NK041(di)004:221: dang po thams cad bar khyams la //
NK041(di)004:222: gnyis kun dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:224: gsum kun phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK041(di)004:225: d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab bo //
NK041(di)004:226: nang sgo brgyad po'i thig rim ni //
NK041(di)004:227: tshangs ngos g.yas g.yon khyams tshad de //
NK041(di)004:228: btab pa tshad bgo de phyed phyir //
NK041(di)004:229: slar yang khyams kyi bzhi cha bsnan //
NK041(di)004:230: phyi sgo dgu pa tshangs ngos su //
NK041(di)004:231: rang gi cha chen gnyis gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:232: nang ma phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK041(di)004:233: phyi ma cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK041(di)004:234: sgo khyud 'gram log mun pa dang //
NK041(di)004:235: ka ba ka rgyan rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:236: de nas mda' thig phyi rol du //
NK041(di)004:237: phyi ma'i sgo tshad gsum bcad la //
NK041(di)004:238: rta bab snam bu brgyad ma'i tshad //
NK041(di)004:239: sgyu 'phrul bzhin las khyad par ni //
NK041(di)004:240: 'og gzhi sna tshogs rdo rjer mdzad //
NK041(di)004:241: mda' rtse zlum bskor nyi gdan te //
NK041(di)004:242: de phyir cha phran gnyis pa'i rig 'dzin gyi snam bu dgos so //
NK041(di)004:243: kha dog ser po la thig le grangs mang bkod /
NK041(di)004:246: phyed dang gcig bskor pad+ma dang //
NK041(di)004:247: dur khrod rdo ra me ri 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:248: rtsa thig nang du cha chen khyams //
NK041(di)004:249: gru chad nang du zlum por bskor //
NK041(di)004:250: de nang mu khyud cha phran bskor //
NK041(di)004:251: de nas lte ba'i bar phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:252: phyi ma rtsibs brgyad nang ma ni //
NK041(di)004:253: cha gsum bgos nas rim bzhin bskor //
NK041(di)004:254: gru chad phyi rol glo 'bur ni //
NK041(di)004:255: cha phran dkyus su cha chen gcig /
NK041(di)004:256: de rnams 'dus pa'i thig rim ste //
NK041(di)004:257: la la zhi dkyil dbus bcug cing //
NK041(di)004:258: phyi rol rig 'dzin khyams spar nas //
NK041(di)004:259: sgo sbrags bcu gcig mdzad pa dang //
NK041(di)004:260: kha cig lte ba cha gsum du //
NK041(di)004:261: bgos pa'i nang ma ling tshe dgu //
NK041(di)004:262: de'i phyir 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang //
NK041(di)004:263: rtsibs brgyad rnams su 'dod pa'ang yod //
NK041(di)004:265: legs mthun rang gi bla ma'i lung //
NK041(di)004:266: dong sprugs brgya ldan dkyil 'khor ni //
NK041(di)004:267: rta bab nas bzung rtsa thig bar //
NK041(di)004:268: sngar gyi sgyu 'phrul zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)004:269: 'khor yug khro bo lta bu las //
NK041(di)004:270: dbus kyi lha gnas lte ba nas //
NK041(di)004:271: rtsa thig la reg bskor ba'i nang //
NK041(di)004:272: cha phran gcig bskor gdung zlum thig /
NK041(di)004:273: gdung thig nas ni lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:274: cha mnyam drug bgos zlum bskor lnga //
NK041(di)004:275: dbus kyi nang mthar cha phran bskor //
NK041(di)004:276: rim bzhin lte ba mu khyud dang //
NK041(di)004:278: 'dab ma bcu drug so gnyis dang //
NK041(di)004:280: la la sgo rkyang 'gram logs dang //
NK041(di)004:281: bral zhing rta bab brgyad po yang //
NK041(di)004:282: cha phran gcig dang phyed phyed dang //
NK041(di)004:283: gnyis dang phyed dang phyed gnyis dang //
NK041(di)004:284: gcig gcig de bzhin 'og bzhi yang //
NK041(di)004:285: sna tshogs rdo rjer bzhed pa yod //
NK041(di)004:286: rta bab brgyad ma'i gdab tshul las //
NK041(di)004:288: tshogs chen 'dus pa dong sprugs kyi //
NK041(di)004:289: thig gi rim pa bshad zin to //
NK041(di)004:290: gnyis pa rta bab bzhi ma ni //
NK041(di)004:291: 'dab thig phyi ru cha chen gnyis //
NK041(di)004:292: nang ma cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK041(di)004:293: rta bab snam bu bzhi yin no //
NK041(di)004:294: phyi ma dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:296: rta bab phyi mtha'i rim pa yang //
NK041(di)004:297: dang po ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam //
NK041(di)004:298: de rjes gsum po re re thung //
NK041(di)004:299: mig gsum bskor tshul rta bab kyi //
NK041(di)004:300: snam bu gnyis pa'i phyi thig dang //
NK041(di)004:301: tshangs thig 'dzom pa nas bzung ste //
NK041(di)004:302: cha phran gnyis gcig kyi dbus ma bskor //
NK041(di)004:303: snam bu dang po'i phyi thig dang //
NK041(di)004:304: tshangs thig 'dzom pa'i g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)004:305: cha phran gnyis re phyin pa nas //
NK041(di)004:306: cha phran gcig re g.yas g.yon bskor //
NK041(di)004:307: yang na g.yas g.yon mig gnyis po //
NK041(di)004:308: brgyad ma lta bu bskor ba'ang yod //
NK041(di)004:309: sna tshogs rdo rje'i ra bskor tshul //
NK041(di)004:310: tshangs phyir gsum phyin mda' phyir gcig /
NK041(di)004:311: phyin te ka rgyan rtse nas bskor //
NK041(di)004:312: de nas phred gnyis phyi ru gcig /
NK041(di)004:313: phyin te snga ma'i tshad des bskor //
NK041(di)004:314: mda' thig rtse nas phyi rol du //
NK041(di)004:315: cha chen phyed dang gcig dang phyed //
NK041(di)004:316: gcig bskor pad+ma dur khrod dang //
NK041(di)004:317: rdo ra me ri rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:318: lte ba'i lha gnas 'gyur tshul ni //
NK041(di)004:319: gu ru zhi drag tshe dpag med //
NK041(di)004:320: rdor sems bzhi la khyams mi dgos //
NK041(di)004:321: de phyir rtsa thig nang du ni //
NK041(di)004:322: zlum bskor so so'i dbye ba bshad //
NK041(di)004:323: bla ma zhi bar lte ba nas //
NK041(di)004:324: rtsa thig la reg zlum por bskor //
NK041(di)004:325: de nang cha phran phyi'i mu khyud //
NK041(di)004:326: mu khyud de nas lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:327: cha mnyam bzhi bskor nang ma'i nang //
NK041(di)004:328: cha phran gcig gi mu khyud bskor //
NK041(di)004:329: nang nas rim bzhin lte ba dang //
NK041(di)004:330: mu khyud 'dab bzhi rin chen brgyad //
NK041(di)004:331: pad ma 'dab brgyad rtsibs brgyad dang //
NK041(di)004:332: rtsibs rten mu khyud rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:333: bla ma drag por lte ba nas //
NK041(di)004:334: rtsa thog nang gi mu khyud bar //
NK041(di)004:335: cha mnyam gsum bgos bskor ba'i nang //
NK041(di)004:336: cha phran gcig bgos rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:337: lte ba mu khyud 'dab ma bzhi //
NK041(di)004:338: rtsibs bzhi rtsibs rten rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:339: lte ba'i mu khyud nang thig dang //
NK041(di)004:340: shar gyi tshangs thig phrad pa nas //
NK041(di)004:341: lte bar tshad pa'i srad bu yis //
NK041(di)004:342: g.yas dang g.yon du mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:343: de nyid nub kyi tshangs thig dang //
NK041(di)004:345: tshe dpag med ni rtsa thig gi //
NK041(di)004:346: nang gi cha phran mu khyud nas //
NK041(di)004:347: lte ba'i bar du phyed mnyam bskor //
NK041(di)004:348: nang ma'i nang mthar cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)004:349: bskor bas lte ba mu khyud dang //
NK041(di)004:350: pad 'dab brgyad dang mu khyud do //
NK041(di)004:351: rdor sems thugs kyi sgrub pa yang //
NK041(di)004:353: rta bab snam bu brgyad ma ni //
NK041(di)004:354: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba lta bur mdzad //
NK041(di)004:355: gshin rje 'joms byed gru chad nang //
NK041(di)004:356: cha phran gcig bskor rtsibs rten sa //
NK041(di)004:357: de nas lte ba'i bar phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:358: nang ma'i nang mthar cha phran bskor //
NK041(di)004:359: lte bar chos 'byung sngar bzhin bskor //
NK041(di)004:360: rim par chos 'byung zla gam dang //
NK041(di)004:361: thod phreng rtsibs bzhi rtsibs rten no //
NK041(di)004:362: bde 'dus pho brang dgu thig ni //
NK041(di)004:363: lte ba'i lha gnas bskor tshul la //
NK041(di)004:364: rtsa thig nang du cha chen re //
NK041(di)004:365: dor ba gru chad thig tu 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:366: tshangs thig dang ni gru chad thig /
NK041(di)004:367: 'dzom pa'i g.yas g.yon thig rgyud du //
NK041(di)004:368: cha mnyam gsum bgos mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:369: mtshan ma nang ma'i steng bzung nas //
NK041(di)004:370: thig bzhi bsnol btab ling tshe dgu //
NK041(di)004:371: thig bzhi'i phyi dang gru thig phyir //
NK041(di)004:372: cha phran phyed re gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:373: mig mang ris bris rdo rje'i gdung //
NK041(di)004:374: rtsa ba'i tshangs zur thig rnams ni //
NK041(di)004:375: so so'i tshangs thig dang po ste //
NK041(di)004:376: phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor zur nas zur //
NK041(di)004:377: gdung bzhi'i bsnol mtshams steng drang gdab //
NK041(di)004:378: phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor zur thig grub //
NK041(di)004:379: zur gyi ling tshe bzhi po yi //
NK041(di)004:380: zur nas zur du logs bzhin gtub //
NK041(di)004:381: mtshams dkyil tshangs thig gnyis pa 'byung //
NK041(di)004:382: de dag dbus kyi bya rjes steng //
NK041(di)004:383: bsnol te brkyangs nas phyogs bzhir gdab //
NK041(di)004:384: phyogs dkyil tshangs thig gnyis pa dang //
NK041(di)004:385: mtshams dkyil so so'i zur thig 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:386: de rnams zhi khro thun mong thig /
NK041(di)004:387: de nas zhi ba'i thig rim ni //
NK041(di)004:388: dbus dang phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK041(di)004:389: gdung thig bzhi po rang rang gi //
NK041(di)004:390: mda' yab phyi thig nyid du 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:391: mtshams bzhi'i rang rang zur thig dang //
NK041(di)004:392: gdung thig phrad pa nas bzung ste //
NK041(di)004:393: logs thig bzhi gdab mda' thig 'byung //
NK041(di)004:394: de nas dkyil 'khor dgu ka yi //
NK041(di)004:395: mda' thig nas ni lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:396: dum bu gsum bgos sum cha'i phyi gdab rtsa thig go //
NK041(di)004:397: de dang mda' thig bar phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:398: cha chen gnyis 'byung nang ma de //
NK041(di)004:399: dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:400: phyi ma phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK041(di)004:401: sgo ni tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du //
NK041(di)004:402: cha chen re gdab de phyed bgo //
NK041(di)004:403: de mthar cha phran gcig re gdab //
NK041(di)004:404: rtsa thig nang nas lte ba'i bar //
NK041(di)004:405: tshad mnyam zlum thig gnyis bskor ba'i //
NK041(di)004:406: re re'i nang du cha chung bskor //
NK041(di)004:407: lte ba mu khyud rtsibs bzhi dang //
NK041(di)004:408: rtsibs rten mu khyud rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:409: phyi rol sgo rgyan rta bab ni //
NK041(di)004:410: snam bu bzhi ma spyi ltar dang //
NK041(di)004:411: khor yug sgyu 'phrul zhi ba bzhin //
NK041(di)004:413: ling tshe dgu kar rang rang gi //
NK041(di)004:414: gdung thig la reg zlum por bskor //
NK041(di)004:415: de nang cha phran re bskor bas //
NK041(di)004:416: so so'i dam can khor yug 'byung //
NK041(di)004:417: khor yug phyed dang rang rang gi //
NK041(di)004:418: zur thig phrad pa'i steng bzung nas //
NK041(di)004:419: ngos bzhir thig gdab mda' thig yin //
NK041(di)004:420: de nang zhi ba lta bu las //
NK041(di)004:421: khyad par rtsa thig nang du ni //
NK041(di)004:422: cha chen gcig bcad gru chad thig /
NK041(di)004:423: gru chad la reg lte ba yi //
NK041(di)004:424: zlum bskor zhi ba lta bu la //
NK041(di)004:425: lte ba'i mu khyud nang thig dang //
NK041(di)004:426: nub kyi tshangs thig phrad pa nas //
NK041(di)004:427: dbus tshad g.yas g.yon mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:428: de gnyis shar gyi tshangs thig dang //
NK041(di)004:429: sbrel bas chos 'byung rtse shar bstan //
NK041(di)004:430: so so'i lte ba'i chos 'byung dang //
NK041(di)004:431: mu khyud rtsibs bzhi rtsibs rten no //
NK041(di)004:432: de ltar nang dkyil dgu po ni //
NK041(di)004:433: rta bab spangs pa'i sgo rdzogs yin //
NK041(di)004:434: gru chad phyi rol khyams dang sgo //
NK041(di)004:435: rgyan ldan rta bab snam bu ni //
NK041(di)004:436: brgyad ma sgyu 'phrul lta bur mdzad //
NK041(di)004:437: la la rta bab snam bzhi'i steng //
NK041(di)004:438: bum pa chos 'khor gdugs dang bcas //
NK041(di)004:439: mchod rten dbyibs su bzhed pa'ang yod //
NK041(di)004:440: 'on kyang sgo tshad gcig ma la //
NK041(di)004:441: snam phran bzhir bcad bang rim bzhi //
NK041(di)004:442: rgyud kyi dgongs par 'byor ram snyam //
NK041(di)004:443: khor yug gdugs kyi rtse mo nas //
NK041(di)004:444: cha chen phyed pa lan gnyis dang //
NK041(di)004:445: cha chen gcig dang de phyed dang //
NK041(di)004:446: cha chen phyed dang cha chen gcig /
NK041(di)004:447: bskor bas nang nas rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:448: bka' sdod sa dang pad+ma dang //
NK041(di)004:449: dur khrod 'khor lo rtsibs stong pa //
NK041(di)004:450: rdo ra me ri rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:451: phur pa spu gri'i khyad par ni //
NK041(di)004:452: gru chad thig nas zlum por bskor //
NK041(di)004:453: de nang phyi nas rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:454: cha phran gcig dang cha phran phyed //
NK041(di)004:455: cha phran phyed drug cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)004:456: de nang chos 'byung gshin rje ltar //
NK041(di)004:457: bskor bas nang nas rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:458: chos 'byung zla gam thod phreng dang //
NK041(di)004:459: rin chen cha brgyad mu khyud dang //
NK041(di)004:460: me yi phreng ba rnams su 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:461: gru thig phyi ru cha phran re //
NK041(di)004:462: btab pas nang brtsigs thod rim gsum //
NK041(di)004:463: de sgo rgyan med zang thal yin //
NK041(di)004:464: khyams dang phyi sgo la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:465: rta bab bzhi ma spyi ltar las //
NK041(di)004:466: pu shu'i zur nas bskor ba yi //
NK041(di)004:467: phyi rol cha chen phyed dang gcig /
NK041(di)004:468: cha phran gcig dang cha chen gcig /
NK041(di)004:469: bskor bas sgrub khog dngos las pad ra dur khrod dam can rdo ra me ri rnams gsungs so //
NK041(di)004:471: dur khrod rdo ra me rir 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:472: de ltar rta bab brgyad ma dang //
NK041(di)004:473: bzhi ma gnyis kyis khog phub nas //
NK041(di)004:474: nye bar mkho ba'i lha gnas sogs //
NK041(di)004:475: bsgyur tshul 'ga' zhig brjod pa ste //
NK041(di)004:477: thams cad bsnyad par mi nus pas //
NK041(di)004:478: 'dis mtshon rang rang dkyil chog ltar //
NK041(di)004:479: zhib mo'i blo yis bsgyur te dpyad //
NK041(di)004:480: gnyis pa tshon gyi cho ga bshad //
NK041(di)004:481: yon bdag 'khor los sgyur rgyal dang //
NK041(di)004:482: rgyal phran 'bangs kyi go rim bzhin //
NK041(di)004:483: rin po che dang 'bru sman dang //
NK041(di)004:484: sa las byas pa'i kha dog ni //
NK041(di)004:485: lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga ste //
NK041(di)004:486: gtsang ma'i snod blugs rang rigs kyi //
NK041(di)004:487: yig 'bru bris la rang phyogs dgod //
NK041(di)004:488: rigs lnga'i lha bsgom byin brlabs te //
NK041(di)004:489: slob dpon shar du zhal phyogs pas //
NK041(di)004:490: dbus kyi 'gying phur bton pa'i shul //
NK041(di)004:491: lag g.yon mtheb srin gyis bzung ba'i //
NK041(di)004:492: rdul tshon 'byung ba rim brtsegs kyi //
NK041(di)004:493: kha dog go rim nges pas dgang //
NK041(di)004:494: de rjes sor mo 'bru lnga bkod //
NK041(di)004:495: khu tshur g.yon pas dbang ldan nas //
NK041(di)004:496: brtsams te g.yas bskor brtsigs pa'i sar //
NK041(di)004:497: pan reg mdzub gang tshad du bri //
NK041(di)004:498: de la mtshan ldan thod pas 'gebs //
NK041(di)004:499: phyis nas rtsig pa 'dren pa'i dus //
NK041(di)004:500: tshon pra brtags pa'i don bzhag la //
NK041(di)004:501: de nas zhal dbang thob pa yi //
NK041(di)004:502: slob ma rnams kyis rim pa ltar //
NK041(di)004:503: ma mthong rmongs la bstan pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)004:504: tshon rnams rim pa bzhin du dgye //
NK041(di)004:505: ji ltar dgye ba'i rim pa ni //
NK041(di)004:506: thog mar sgyu 'phrul zhi ba la //
NK041(di)004:507: dbus mthing mu khyud 'od zer te //
NK041(di)004:508: rtsibs bzhi mchan dang gru chad dang //
NK041(di)004:509: glo 'bur bar khyams sgo dang bcas //
NK041(di)004:510: shar dkar ba sogs phyogs kyis dbye //
NK041(di)004:511: 'khor lo'i phyi yi mu khyud nag /
NK041(di)004:512: rtsig pa nang nas rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:513: mthing dkar ser dmar ljang gu'o //
NK041(di)004:514: 'dod snam dmar la pha gu ser //
NK041(di)004:515: d+r+wa ba'i gzhi nag d+r+wa ba dkar //
NK041(di)004:516: shar bu'i gzhi sngo shar bu dkar //
NK041(di)004:517: mda' yab dkar po mchod rten ris //
NK041(di)004:518: mun pa pa dang ti glang rgyab gnyis nag /
NK041(di)004:519: ka ba phyogs mdog rgyan mdzes tshon //
NK041(di)004:520: rta bab brgyad rnams go rim bzhin //
NK041(di)004:521: rta rkang gzhi sngo rdo rje ser //
NK041(di)004:522: chu skyes dmar la sgrom mdzes tshon //
NK041(di)004:523: zar tshag dkar la gzhi ma nag /
NK041(di)004:525: sgril 'phyang dkar la gzhi ma nag /
NK041(di)004:526: shar bu dkar la gzhi ma sngo //
NK041(di)004:527: rgya phub khyung mgo mthing kha'o //
NK041(di)004:529: ri dwags gser mdog gdugs dkar po //
NK041(di)004:530: 'og gzhi'i rtsig dang mu khyud bcas //
NK041(di)004:531: phyogs mdog phyi khyams ljang gu ste //
NK041(di)004:532: pad+ma sna tshogs rdo ra mthing //
NK041(di)004:533: me ri sna tshogs chos 'khor ro //
NK041(di)004:534: de nas sgyu 'phrul khro bo yi //
NK041(di)004:535: tshon gyi khyad par cung zad bshad //
NK041(di)004:536: lte ba mthing ga mu khyud ljang //
NK041(di)004:537: rtsibs bzhi ser po gong ras dmar //
NK041(di)004:538: mu khyud mthing ga gru chad ljang //
NK041(di)004:539: yul ma'i khyams ser sgo phyogs mdog /
NK041(di)004:540: nang rtsibs nang nas sngo dmar dkar //
NK041(di)004:541: dbang mo'i khyams dmar sgo phyogs mdog /
NK041(di)004:542: phyi rol dur khrod gzhi ma nag /
NK041(di)004:543: gzhan rnams zhi ba ji bzhin no //
NK041(di)004:544: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i tshon thob ni //
NK041(di)004:545: zhi ba'i tshon ni d+r+wa ba bzhin //
NK041(di)004:546: khro bo'i lte ba'i zlum skor ni //
NK041(di)004:547: gsum ga mthing la rtsibs brgyad ser //
NK041(di)004:548: gong ras dmar la mu khyud sngo //
NK041(di)004:549: gru ljang glo 'bur phyogs kyi mdog /
NK041(di)004:550: bar khyams dang po ser po la //
NK041(di)004:551: gnyis pa dkar la gsum pa dmar //
NK041(di)004:552: bzhi pa ser la lnga pa dmar //
NK041(di)004:553: drug pa dkar la bdun pa nag /
NK041(di)004:554: brgyad pa phyogs mdog dgu pa ljang //
NK041(di)004:555: rtsig pa nang brgyad ljang dgu la //
NK041(di)004:556: phyi rtsig dang ni sgo kun gyi //
NK041(di)004:557: 'dod snam pha gu la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:558: sgyu 'phrul ltar la nyi gdan ljang //
NK041(di)004:559: sna tshogs rdo rje phyogs kyi mdog /
NK041(di)004:560: dur khrod gzhi sogs kun dang mthun /
NK041(di)004:561: dong sprugs dbus mthing mu khyud ser //
NK041(di)004:562: 'dab bzhi phyogs tshon brgyad phan chad //
NK041(di)004:563: lha mdog mdzes tshon gang bde bya //
NK041(di)004:564: mu khyud phyi ma mthing ga ste //
NK041(di)004:565: lhag rnams zhi ba dang mthun no //
NK041(di)004:566: bla ma zhi ba'i tshon thob ni //
NK041(di)004:567: lte ba mthing la mu khyud ljang //
NK041(di)004:568: 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog brgyad sna tshogs //
NK041(di)004:569: rin chen cha brgyad rtsibs brgyad dang //
NK041(di)004:570: mu khyud rnams ni mthing ga'o //
NK041(di)004:571: rta bab snam bu bzhi ma la //
NK041(di)004:572: nang nas dmar sngo ljang ser ram //
NK041(di)004:573: yang na ser mthing dmar ljang bya //
NK041(di)004:574: bla ma drag po'i chos 'byung dmar //
NK041(di)004:575: mu ran sngon po zla gam dmar //
NK041(di)004:576: mu khyud thod pa'i phreng ba la //
NK041(di)004:578: gong ras phyogs mdog mu khyud mthing //
NK041(di)004:579: tshe dpag med kyi lte ba ni //
NK041(di)004:580: dmar po rdor sems dkar po ste //
NK041(di)004:581: gnyis ka'i 'dab ma mdzes tshon no //
NK041(di)004:583: zla gam dmar po thod ras dkar //
NK041(di)004:584: rtsibs bzhi mthing la mchan phyogs mdog /
NK041(di)004:585: mu khyud sngon po gzhan rnams 'dra //
NK041(di)004:586: bde 'dus zhi ba'i tshon rim bshad //
NK041(di)004:587: dkyil 'khor dgu po'i lte ba ni //
NK041(di)004:588: dbus dkar shar dang shar lho sngo //
NK041(di)004:589: lho dang lho nub ser po ste //
NK041(di)004:590: nub dang nub byang dmar po'o //
NK041(di)004:591: byang dang byang shar ljang gu bya //
NK041(di)004:592: kun gyi mu khyud 'od zer la //
NK041(di)004:593: rtsibs bzhi sgo rnams phyogs mdog la //
NK041(di)004:594: rtsig pa rang rang rigs dang sbyar //
NK041(di)004:595: rdo rje'i gdung ni mthing ga'o //
NK041(di)004:596: phyi khyams phyogs mdog rtsig pa ni //
NK041(di)004:597: nang nas dkar mthing ser dmar ljang //
NK041(di)004:599: da ru kad ljang pu shu dkar //
NK041(di)004:600: rta bab bzhi ni mdzes tshon la //
NK041(di)004:601: pad ra'i nang du phyogs skyong gi //
NK041(di)004:602: snam bu dkar po byas kyang rung //
NK041(di)004:603: pad ra sna tshogs rdo ra nag /
NK041(di)004:605: khro bo'i pho brang dgu po yi //
NK041(di)004:606: tshon ni lte ba'i chos 'byung rnams //
NK041(di)004:607: dbus mthing shar nas g.yas bskor du //
NK041(di)004:608: mthing ga sngon po ser po dkar //
NK041(di)004:609: dmar mthing ljang gu nag po'o //
NK041(di)004:610: kun kyang rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK041(di)004:611: mthing ga gru chad khyams sgo sogs //
NK041(di)004:612: phyogs mdog rtsig pa thod rim gsum //
NK041(di)004:614: dam can khor yug nag po dang //
NK041(di)004:615: rdo rje'i gdung mthing 'og gzhi sngo //
NK041(di)004:616: 'bar ba'i rgyan gyis thams cad spras //
NK041(di)004:617: dbang mo'i lha khyams phyogs mdog la //
NK041(di)004:618: rtsig pa 'dod snam la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:619: sgyu 'phrul lta bur byas pa las //
NK041(di)004:620: khor yug bka' sdod khrag mtsho dang //
NK041(di)004:622: phur pa spu gri'i tshon yig ni //
NK041(di)004:623: gru gsum mthing nag zla gam dmar //
NK041(di)004:624: thod ra dkar la rgya chad mthing //
NK041(di)004:625: mu bskor ser po mun mchan dmar //
NK041(di)004:626: khyud bskor me ri lnga ldan te //
NK041(di)004:627: khyams smug nang rtsig dkar dmar sngo //
NK041(di)004:628: sgo khyams phyi rtsig la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:629: spyi 'gre ltar las khor yug gi //
NK041(di)004:630: dam can gnas ni khrag matsho'o //
NK041(di)004:631: de ltar dkyil 'khor so so yi //
NK041(di)004:632: lha gnas rnams su mtshan ma ni //
NK041(di)004:633: grub na rang rang sku gzugs dang //
NK041(di)004:635: gal te de tsam ma grub na //
NK041(di)004:636: sku mdog dang mtshungs tshon spungs bya //
NK041(di)004:637: mdor na so so'i dkyil chog ltar //
NK041(di)004:638: tshon rtsi mi 'thug mi srab cing //
NK041(di)004:639: ma 'dres chad dang yo ba sogs //
NK041(di)004:640: spangs te sgrin po'i blo yis bri //
NK041(di)004:641: gang zhig blo gros dman rnams kyis //
NK041(di)004:642: thig tshon bya ba gang la yang //
NK041(di)004:643: rtsing po'i spyod pas skyon byung na //
NK041(di)004:644: de bsal cho ga brtsam par bya //
NK041(di)004:645: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab //
NK041(di)004:646: yin phyir rtog ge'i yul min pas //
NK041(di)004:647: rgyud 'grel bla ma'i man ngag bzhin //
NK041(di)004:648: rang bzo spangs nas bris pa 'di //
NK041(di)004:649: gter chen chos rje'i bka' 'bangs su //
NK041(di)004:651: dge bas mtha' yas 'gro ba kun //
NK041(di)004:652: bde ba chen po'i sku thob shog /
NK041(di)004:656: da ni thig tshon gyi cho ga de dag don cung zad bkrol te bshad par bya'o //
NK041(di)004:657: 'di la thig dang tshon gyi bya ba gnyis /
NK041(di)004:666: dang po skud rgyu zhi ba la me tog pad+ma'i rgyus pa dang /
NK041(di)004:667: khro bo la zhing gi rgyus chen la bya bar gsungs kyang /
NK041(di)004:668: thun mong du ras bal gtsang ma dpa' bo'i rin
NK041(di)004:669: zhes pa rin la ma rtsod pa nyos la bu
NK041(di)004:670: mo mtshan ldan lo bcu drug mas bkal ba'i snal
NK041(di)004:671: ma kha dog lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga ste /
NK041(di)004:672: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba rdo rje las rim las /
NK041(di)004:673: pad+ma'i rgyus la kha dog bsgyur //
NK041(di)004:674: bcu drug phyag rgyas legs bkal te //
NK041(di)004:675: snal ma gcig la lnga lngar ldan //
NK041(di)004:676: ye shes rang bzhin shes par bya //
NK041(di)004:679: ba su ta yi rgyus chen la //
NK041(di)004:680: dam tshig ye shes sku gsum lnga //
NK041(di)004:681: zhes ba su ta dam tshig dang /
NK041(di)004:682: rgyus chen ye shes kyi rgyur gsungs so //
NK041(di)004:683: zhi khro thun mong du ras bal la bya bar rung ba ni /
NK041(di)004:684: phur pa'i pad+ma las rim las /
NK041(di)004:685: de rjes dkyil 'khor thig gdab brtsam //
NK041(di)004:686: shes rab mtshan dang ldan pa des //
NK041(di)004:687: skyon med ras bal bsgyur ba yi //
NK041(di)004:688: kha dog lnga ni bkal byas te //
NK041(di)004:690: h+aum k+aa ra'i yang dag gi dkyil chog las kyang /
NK041(di)004:691: thig skud ras gsar pa'i rgyu las byung ba sngags kyis byin gyis brlabs nas bkal bar bya ste /
NK041(di)004:694: ring thung dkyil 'khor gyi nyis 'gyur te /
NK041(di)004:695: dkyil 'khor khru gang ba la gdab pa'i thig skud ni khru do pa yin no //
NK041(di)004:696: 'dir nyis 'gyur bya rgyu'i dkyil 'khor gyi don sh+rad+d+h+aasa rtsa thig la ngos bzung nas /
NK041(di)004:697: de nyis 'gyur sna tshogs rdo rje'i rtse tshun chad
NK041(di)004:698: kyi tshad du byas te rta babs sgo tshad gcig
NK041(di)004:700: phreng ba mkhan po'i dkyil 'khor mda' thig la byas nas /
NK041(di)004:701: de nyis 'gyur dur khrod spangs pa'i 'od phreng tshun
NK041(di)004:702: gyi tshad du byas te rta bab sgo tshad gsum
NK041(di)004:703: mar 'dod la / 'dir rta bab sgo tshad gnyis
NK041(di)004:704: mar byas pa'i tshe phyi ma ltar khas blangs pas
NK041(di)004:705: dur khrod yod pa'i phyogs la 'grigs shing /
NK041(di)004:706: dur khrod med pa'i phyogs la snga ma ltar byas
NK041(di)004:707: na de nyis 'gyur gyis rwa rtse'am 'og gzhi'i 'khor
NK041(di)004:709: phyi ma ltar na sgo tshad gnyis kyis ma langs mod kyi /
NK041(di)004:710: 'on kyang nyis 'gyur du bya bar gsungs pa ni
NK041(di)004:711: dkyil 'khor dang 'tshams par bya zhes pa'i don yin
NK041(di)004:712: pa'i gnad kyis / 'od phreng dag gi phyi rol
NK041(di)004:713: du thig ro ma lus par gdab dgos pa'i phyir
NK041(di)004:714: pa'i gnad kyis / na / slob dpon dang thig
NK041(di)004:715: g.yog gis lag pas bzung ba'i cha ma gtogs pa
NK041(di)004:716: mtha'i khor yug gi tshad la ring ba mi rung
NK041(di)004:717: pa'i gnad kyis / na / zhing / gzhan du
NK041(di)004:718: zlum thig ni rkyang thig la ltos mi dgos pa'i
NK041(di)004:719: pa'i gnad kyis / na / zhing / phyir / rta babs sgo tshad gsum ma dang /
NK041(di)004:721: gcig ma gsum gang byed kyang rung ste /
NK041(di)004:722: 'og gzhi'i rwa rtse tshun gyi tshad dang mnyam tsam
NK041(di)004:723: gyis kyang dgos pa 'grub cing de las thung du
NK041(di)004:724: mi rung ngo // sbom phra ni sgo'i nyi shu'i
NK041(di)004:725: cha ste rtsig pa'i re kh+aa dang mnyam pas cha
NK041(di)004:727: de skad du'ang galpo dang mnyam sbyor gyi dkyil chog las /
NK041(di)004:729: sbom phra sgo yi nyi shu cha //
NK041(di)004:732: skud pa rnams dpa' bo 'bru lngar mos la /
NK041(di)004:733: mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs pa'i rgyal ba rnams 'bar ba'i lta stangs kyis bskul bas /
NK041(di)004:734: sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang sems ye shes lnga'i rang
NK041(di)004:735: bzhin 'od lnga'i rnam par byung ba thig skud la
NK041(di)004:736: phog pas ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin can du gyur
NK041(di)004:737: par bsam la / dang po srad bu lnga so so dang /
NK041(di)004:738: de nas gcig tu sgril ba sogs so so'i dkyil chog ltar bya ba gces so //
NK041(di)004:739: de dag kyang mnyam sbyor dkyil chog las /
NK041(di)004:740: rin chen thod pa'i snod bzhag la //
NK041(di)004:741: rigs kyi yi ge'i sngags kyis bskyed //
NK041(di)004:744: mig gi lta ba bkug byas pa'i //
NK041(di)004:745: sangs rgyas rigs rnams gzhug par bya //
NK041(di)004:746: nyi zla 'bar ba'i lcags kyu yis //
NK041(di)004:747: de gnyis gcig tu gnas par bsgom //
NK041(di)004:748: mchod 'bul bstod pas mnyes byas nas //
NK041(di)004:749: gtso bo'i sngags brjod bsgril bar bya //
NK041(di)004:751: zhi ba rdo rje las rim las /
NK041(di)004:752: gtsang ma'i snod du legs bkod de //
NK041(di)004:753: nyi zla 'bar ba'i gdan dag la //
NK041(di)004:754: thugs las yi ge 'bru grangs bzhin //
NK041(di)004:755: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mdun drangs te //
NK041(di)004:756: mchod sbyar gsol ba gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:757: sbyor ba'i ye shes grangs mnyam dang //
NK041(di)004:758: rdo rje gsum byin nges par bstim //
NK041(di)004:759: dang po rang bzhin mnyam byas te //
NK041(di)004:760: cung zad mchod la brtag par bya //
NK041(di)004:761: zhes yi dam thun mong gi byin rlabs gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK041(di)004:763: rdo rje rgyal po lhar gsal bas gzungs ma'am /
NK041(di)004:764: slob ma yum du mos pa la dzahdzahzhesa blangs te /
NK041(di)004:765: thig byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkar breng gis byung bar bsam la /
NK041(di)004:766: rang gi mthe bong dang gung mo 'og tu phyogs
NK041(di)004:767: pas thig skud bzung zhing gcus te nam mkha' la
NK041(di)004:768: gyen du se gol gyis gdab steng phyogs su ye
NK041(di)004:769: shes kyi gzhal yas khang du gyur par bsam /
NK041(di)004:770: yang 'og tu phyogs te bar snang la gdab pas
NK041(di)004:771: 'og gi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang du gyur par
NK041(di)004:773: ye shes lnga ldan gnam thig gis //
NK041(di)004:779: gdab tshul slob dpon nub tu 'dug /
NK041(di)004:781: bde 'dus zhi ba'i thig chog slob dpon gyis mdzad pa las /
NK041(di)004:782: slob dpon chu bdag phyogs gnas la //
NK041(di)004:783: slob ma brgya byin phyogs gnas te //
NK041(di)004:784: tshangs thig dang po gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:785: gshin rje gnod sbyin phyogs gnas te //
NK041(di)004:786: tshangs thig gnyis pa gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:787: me dang 'byung por gnas nas ni //
NK041(di)004:788: shar gyi thig ni gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:789: rlung dang bden bral phyogs gnas te //
NK041(di)004:790: nub kyi phyogs ni de bzhin gdab //
NK041(di)004:791: slob dpon rlung gnas byang gi thig /
NK041(di)004:792: me dang bden bral gnas nas lho //
NK041(di)004:793: mtshams kyi thig gnyis de bzhin gdab //
NK041(di)004:796: de nas slob dpon chu bdag 'dug /
NK041(di)004:797: shi sha brgya byin phyogs su 'dug /
NK041(di)004:798: gnam thig tshangs thig dang po gdab //
NK041(di)004:800: zur thig gnyis kyang shes par bya //
NK041(di)004:803: rdo rje dril bu thogs la gdab //
NK041(di)004:804: sgra rnams kyang ni bkrol bar bya //
NK041(di)004:805: ye shes thig gdab rim pa'o //
NK041(di)004:806: zhes gsungs pas rdor dril dang bcas pas phyogs ma 'khrul bar gdab cing /
NK041(di)004:809: blo ldan rgyab kyis 'gro bar bya /
NK041(di)004:811: tshangs thig dang logs thig la g.yas bskor rgyab 'gros kyis 'gro zhing /
NK041(di)004:812: zur thig gnyis la skor phyogs su 'gro ba las rgyab 'gros mi dgos so //
NK041(di)004:820: zhi ba la ras bal lam /
NK041(di)004:821: khro bo la zhing chen gyi rgyu ma'am /
NK041(di)004:822: gzhan las ro skra la'ang bya bar bshad do //
NK041(di)004:824: shi ba'i skra yi skud pa'am //
NK041(di)004:825: ba su ta yis thig skud bya //
NK041(di)004:828: kha dog gsum ldan snal ma dgu //
NK041(di)004:829: ras bal las bkal sku gsung thugs //
NK041(di)004:831: 'on kyang zhi khro thun mong du ras bal gtsang
NK041(di)004:832: ma mtshan ldan mas bkal ba'i skud pa kha dog
NK041(di)004:833: sum sgril lam dgu sgril du byas pa /
NK041(di)004:834: tshad kyang sngar dang 'dra ba ste /
NK041(di)004:836: de rjes las thig brtsam par bya //
NK041(di)004:837: nyes pa'i skyon med ras bal dkar //
NK041(di)004:838: mtshan ldan gzungs ma gong mas bkal //
NK041(di)004:839: shin tu snyoms la 'jur mdud med //
NK041(di)004:841: sbom phra sgo yi nyi shu cha //
NK041(di)004:844: skud pa rnams 'bru gsum du mos la //
NK041(di)004:845: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi gnas gsum las 'od
NK041(di)004:846: zer dkar dmar mthing gsum byung ba thig skud la
NK041(di)004:847: thim pas de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs gsum mam
NK041(di)004:848: dgu phrug gi rang bzhin du gyur par bsam ste
NK041(di)004:850: sa thig gsum sgril sku gsung thugs //
NK041(di)004:853: dri bzang po bdud rtsi lnga dang bcas pa'i dkar
NK041(di)004:854: chal gyis sbags pa'i thig skud brkyangs te slob dpon
NK041(di)004:855: slob ma lha yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams
NK041(di)004:856: nas dam tshig gi thig sku gsung thugs kyi rang
NK041(di)004:857: bzhin can btab par bsam la rdor dril bzhag ste
NK041(di)004:858: thig chen brgyad po bskor phyogs dang go rim ye
NK041(di)004:859: thig bzhin du byas nas gdab ste /
NK041(di)004:861: rdo rje dril bu bor nas ni //
NK041(di)004:862: gdab pa'i rim pa gong ltar bya //
NK041(di)004:864: yang gnas skabs bya sla ba'i ched du logs bzhi'i
NK041(di)004:865: sngon du zur thig gnyis btab kyang mi 'gal te
NK041(di)004:866: / rdo rje gur gyi le'u brgyad par /
NK041(di)004:867: dang po tshangs pa'i thig dang ni //
NK041(di)004:868: gnyis par mtshams kyi thig dang ni //
NK041(di)004:869: gsum par ngos ni bzhi pa'i thig /
NK041(di)004:870: thig ni rab tu gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:872: de yang gnam sa'i thig gdab pa'i tshe /
NK041(di)004:875: phyogs 'khrul ba'i skyon rnams sgrim po'i blos spangs nas gdab ste /
NK041(di)004:877: mkhas ldan chen pos sgrim ste bya //
NK041(di)004:880: thig skud chad na slob dpon 'chi //
NK041(di)004:881: phyogs 'khrul bas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK041(di)004:882: rgyun chad lam la gnas par 'gyur //
NK041(di)004:883: de phyir mkhas pas sgrim ste bya //
NK041(di)004:885: bde 'dus kyi dkyil 'khor bya ba'i las rim las kyang /
NK041(di)004:886: thig skud chad na slob dpon la ngan zur thig
NK041(di)004:887: nyams na slob ma 'chi ring thung 'chor na na
NK041(di)004:888: bar 'gyur phyogs mtshams 'khrugs na nyes par 'gyur zhes
NK041(di)004:889: gsungs so // yang las rim las /
NK041(di)004:890: kun tu bya bar byas pa dang ting 'dzin ldan
NK041(di)004:891: pas ye shes las ye shes thim pa des mchod
NK041(di)004:892: de dam tshig phyag rgya muhyisa gshegs de nas nyes
NK041(di)004:893: pa gang yang med zhes pas thig skud gnyis la
NK041(di)004:894: gtang rag gi tshul du ye shes la ye shes
NK041(di)004:895: thim par bsam la mchod de dam tshig gi phyag
NK041(di)004:896: rgya bcas la badz+ra muhzhesa pas gshegs su gsol /
NK041(di)004:897: de ltar byas pas thig skud la 'gom pa sogs thal kyang nyes pa mi 'byung ngo //
NK041(di)004:898: de bzhin du dkyil 'khor la btab pa'i thig rab
NK041(di)004:899: gnas dang ldan pa de la'ang 'gom pa'i nyes pa
NK041(di)004:900: sel ba'i phyir h+r+aihzhesa sgra ring por brjod par dkyil
NK041(di)004:901: 'khor gyi thig lha blos nam mkha' la btegs nas
NK041(di)004:902: thig phran gyi cha dbye ba dang /
NK041(di)004:903: tshon bkye ba sogs thig gi 'og tu 'dzul bar mos nas bya bar gsungs te /
NK041(di)004:905: rab gnas ldan pa'i thig 'gom na //
NK041(di)004:906: bde gshegs skur pa btab dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)004:907: sangs rgyas chos las ring 'gyur bas //
NK041(di)004:910: gnam sa'i thig gdab pa'i go rim kyang /
NK041(di)004:912: thog mar las thig btab nas /
NK041(di)004:913: de rjes sku gsung thugs re re ye shes lnga
NK041(di)004:914: lnga'i ro dang ldan par bsam la ye thig 'debs
NK041(di)004:916: 'dir ye thig thog mar 'chad pa brjod pa nyung bas 'chad bde ba dang /
NK041(di)004:917: der ma zad sgyu 'phrul las kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK041(di)004:918: bi ma las thig gi pin+da tha las /
NK041(di)004:919: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor gnam thig gdab //
NK041(di)004:920: de nas sa thig 'chad pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:921: nyes pa bral bar gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:922: yang na ye shes dam tshig pa'i //
NK041(di)004:923: rjes la rab gnas gdan phyir gdab //
NK041(di)004:924: ces snga phyi 'dam khar gsungs pa dang /
NK041(di)004:925: tshad ldan gyi gzhung mang por ye thig sngon la 'debs pa'i khungs kyang mthong ba'i phyir ro //
NK041(di)004:927: thig g.yog las kyi sems ma ste //
NK041(di)004:928: mtshan ldan byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK041(di)004:929: phyag rgya gar dang bcas pa yis //
NK041(di)004:930: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor gnam thig gdab //
NK041(di)004:931: de nas sa thig gdab pa yang //
NK041(di)004:932: 'dul ba'i dbang gi bye brag las //
NK041(di)004:933: man+dala tshad ni nges pa med //
NK041(di)004:934: sor bzhi pa las brtsams nas ni //
NK041(di)004:935: ji srid dpag tshad thug bar ro //
NK041(di)004:937: bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa'i rtsa rgyud las /
NK041(di)004:938: dang por nam mkhar dgongs thig gdab //
NK041(di)004:939: de nas sa thig rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:942: ye shes thig gdab rim pa'o //
NK041(di)004:943: de rjes las thig brtsam par bya //
NK041(di)004:945: 'on kyang 'dir spyir btang tsam du bkod pa ste /
NK041(di)004:946: bye brag dkyil chog so so'i lugs bzhin ma 'dres par lag tu len pa gces so //
NK041(di)004:947: de ltar thig gdab spyir bshad pas khog phub nas /
NK041(di)004:948: da ni las thig gi cha dbye ba sogs 'chad par 'dod pas /
NK041(di)004:949: de yang cung zad phye ste bshad //
NK041(di)004:951: de la thog mar thig gzhi stegs bu'i tshad ni
NK041(di)004:952: phyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad sngar drangs ma thag pa'i
NK041(di)004:953: rngam glog gi lung de las /
NK041(di)004:954: sor bzhi nas dpag tshad kyi bar ma nges par gsungs pa ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan dang /
NK041(di)004:955: ting nge 'dzin ma phye ba'i skabs te /
NK041(di)004:957: yang na rgyangs grags dpag tshad dam //
NK041(di)004:958: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas pa //
NK041(di)004:959: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor sna tshogs bsgom //
NK041(di)004:962: rgyangs grags tsam ni dpag tshad sbyor //
NK041(di)004:963: mkha' dbyings bsam mi khyab pa ru //
NK041(di)004:964: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor bsam par bya //
NK041(di)004:965: zhes lhag pa ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du gsungs shing /
NK041(di)004:966: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la chung 'bring che gsum las /
NK041(di)004:968: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK041(di)004:969: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK041(di)004:972: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK041(di)004:973: yang na khru ni bcu drug go //
NK041(di)004:976: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lnga bya //
NK041(di)004:978: 'dir khru gang tshad las mi chung ba'i zhes smras pa ni /
NK041(di)004:979: de chung tshad yin pas de las chung du mi btub pa'i tha tshig go //
NK041(di)004:980: stegs bu de'i rnam pa ni /
NK041(di)004:982: mtha' kun nas snyoms pa ste /
NK041(di)004:983: 'on kyang shar mtho na tshe thung /
NK041(di)004:985: ces gsungs pas shar dang byang cung zad dma' bar bya'o //
NK041(di)004:986: ji ltar rigs pa'i sogs ni tshangs thig zur la
NK041(di)004:987: sogs pa'i thig gdab tshul thams cad zhib mor ston
NK041(di)004:988: pa ste klog pas grub pa'o //
NK041(di)004:989: gdab tshul rnam pa gzhan du na 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK041(di)004:990: thog mar tshangs thig dang po gdab //
NK041(di)004:991: de dbus tshad btab dkyil 'khor dkyil //
NK041(di)004:992: de steng bzung nas zlum bskor gcig /
NK041(di)004:993: de dang tshangs thig phrad sa ru //
NK041(di)004:994: bzung ste snga ma'i srad bu las //
NK041(di)004:995: cung zad ring ngam thung du bcug /
NK041(di)004:996: de yis gar slebs zlum bskor de'i //
NK041(di)004:997: phyi dang nang du phyogs zur gyi //
NK041(di)004:998: bya rjes de steng tshangs thig dang //
NK041(di)004:999: zur thig gnyis pa gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:1000: dbus nas phyogs rer zur thig steng //
NK041(di)004:1001: cha mnyam dgu yi mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:1002: de steng logs rer cha chen ni //
NK041(di)004:1003: dgu dgu bco brgyad gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:1004: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK041(di)004:1005: gnyis pa cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1006: gsum pa bzhi pa mi gdab bzhag /
NK041(di)004:1007: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:1008: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK041(di)004:1009: bdun pa brgyad pa bzhi bzhir bgo //
NK041(di)004:1010: dgu pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:1011: ces rta bab brgyad ma dang /
NK041(di)004:1013: cha mnyam brgyad kyi mtshan ma bya //
NK041(di)004:1015: brgyad brgyad bcu drug gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:1017: bdun pa bzhir bgo brgyad dbus dor //
NK041(di)004:1020: dgu dgu bco brgyad gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:1021: de la cha chen nang ma gsum //
NK041(di)004:1022: phyed du gtubs te drug tu bya //
NK041(di)004:1023: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK041(di)004:1024: gnyis pa'i nang du cha phran gcig /
NK041(di)004:1025: gsum bzhi mi gdab lnga dbus dor //
NK041(di)004:1026: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK041(di)004:1027: de ni nang gi sgo yin no //
NK041(di)004:1028: cha chen bzhi pa phyi yi khyams //
NK041(di)004:1029: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK041(di)004:1031: gzhan du bris pa las 'dir bya sla'o //
NK041(di)004:1032: 'on kyang gzhung du thog mar mda' thig nas 'debs pa ni /
NK041(di)004:1033: rtsa thig sogs ngos bzung ste go ba la phan pa'i ched dang /
NK041(di)004:1034: mnyam sbyor gyi dkyil chog las kyang /
NK041(di)004:1035: thig ni phyi nas btab pa la //
NK041(di)004:1036: tshon rtsi nang nas bkye bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1037: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa'ang yin no //
NK041(di)004:1038: yang cha chen bco brgyad dang bcu drug tu dbye ba 'di ni /
NK041(di)004:1040: phyogs rer dgu dgu ste so drug gi steng tshangs zur rtsis te /
NK041(di)004:1041: mchog gi thig phran bzhi bcu bzhi //
NK041(di)004:1042: legs par kha dog phye yang rung //
NK041(di)004:1045: thig ni bcu drug dag tu gdab ces dang /
NK041(di)004:1047: ngos bzhi'i cha ni dbye byas te //
NK041(di)004:1048: re re'ang cha chen bcu drug tu //
NK041(di)004:1049: so sor rnam par dbye bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1050: zhes gsungs pa'i don te spyir bshad pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1051: bye brag rta babs brgyad ma dang /
NK041(di)004:1052: bzhi ma las 'phros te dkyil 'khor so so'i thig bshad pa las /
NK041(di)004:1053: thog mar sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i thig gdab tshul 'di ni dkyil 'khor 'bring po'i 'debs tshul te /
NK041(di)004:1054: bsdus pa la bar khyams med pa'i gru chad la sgo gtod pa dang /
NK041(di)004:1055: rgyas par pho brang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba
NK041(di)004:1056: dang bcas pa re re la'ang rtsibs bzhi lte ba
NK041(di)004:1058: 'di'i rta babs brgyad ma'i 'god rim dang /
NK041(di)004:1059: 'god gzhi 'khor lo byed pa zhi ba la khor
NK041(di)004:1060: yug gsum las mi byed pa sogs kyi don ni
NK041(di)004:1061: 'byams klas par / zhi ba 'bring po'i blos bslang
NK041(di)004:1062: rnam bzhag tu bris yod pas spro na der blta
NK041(di)004:1063: 'byams klas par / bar bya ste / khro bo yang des khog phub pa yod do //
NK041(di)004:1065: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings steng dang /
NK041(di)004:1066: tshogs chen 'dus pa 'og khang du byas pa'i khro
NK041(di)004:1067: bo la sgo dgu brtsegs su byed pa ni h'u
NK041(di)004:1068: k+aa ra'i rgya mdud 'grel pa las /
NK041(di)004:1069: gzhal yas khang mtha' thug pa med pa'i khyams dgu las me dpung 'bar ba ni /
NK041(di)004:1070: theg pa dgu'i rtogs pa'i ye shes dgu yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir sgo dgu brtsegs su mthong ste /
NK041(di)004:1071: khyams mtho dman gyi chas brtsegs pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1073: spyir sgo dgur gyur ba ni phyogs dang po'i dbang gis shar nas smos pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1074: brtsegs pa ni sgo rim pa dgu par 'og gzhi'i chas phye ba'o //
NK041(di)004:1075: de dag la thig nyi shu rtsa bdun no //
NK041(di)004:1076: zhes gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas bris pa ste rang gi rje bla ma'i dgongs pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1077: de'ang 'di'i dbus kyi zlum skor gsum ni /
NK041(di)004:1078: che mchog dang dbang mchog badz+ra he ru ka gsum gyi sa'o //
NK041(di)004:1079: de nas rim par rtsibs brgyad la rgyud lung gi khro bo brgyad /
NK041(di)004:1081: gru chad la goo r+ai ma brgyad /
NK041(di)004:1082: bar khyams dang por sim ha ma brgyad dang /
NK041(di)004:1083: de'i sgor nang gi sgo ma bzhi /
NK041(di)004:1084: gnyis par spor ma brgyad dang /
NK041(di)004:1086: gsum par dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK041(di)004:1088: lnga par ma bdun sring bzhi /
NK041(di)004:1090: bdun par khro bo drug cu /
NK041(di)004:1091: brgyad par pho nya sum brgya drug cu /
NK041(di)004:1092: dgu par ma mo drug cu /
NK041(di)004:1093: phyogs bzhi'i rta bab la rig 'dzin rnams bzhugs par bshad do //
NK041(di)004:1094: la la ni zhi dkyil dbus su bcug pa'i sgo
NK041(di)004:1095: sbrags bcu gcig tu mdzad pa sogs la khungs gsal
NK041(di)004:1096: po ma mthong / khro dkyil gyi gtso bo 'god sa mi rnyed pa'i skyon gnas so //
NK041(di)004:1097: yang slob dpon sh+aan+ta rak+shi tas mdzad pa'i kun 'dus kyi ber ka yig chung las /
NK041(di)004:1098: gzhal yas sgo dgu brtsegs gru chad gnyis sgo snam khyams lnga la yod pa brgyad /
NK041(di)004:1099: gcig mu khyud la yod na mu khyud zlum po la sgo gdong du 'tshal la bsam /
NK041(di)004:1100: zhes rags pa bkod pa dang /
NK041(di)004:1102: 'khor lo drug brtsegs rdo rje mu khyud bdun du 'dod pa'ang yod gsungs te /
NK041(di)004:1103: de dag sngon gyi mkhas pa rnams kyis ma bkral
NK041(di)004:1104: bas gya tshoms su bya bar rigs pa ma yin
NK041(di)004:1105: no // 'dir thig gi cha gsum nang ma 'khor lo dang /
NK041(di)004:1106: phyi ma gnyis ka bsdoms te cha lngar bgos pa'i nang ma bzhis sgo brgyad dang /
NK041(di)004:1107: phyi mas phyi sgor 'gyur ba'i phyag len 'di ni
NK041(di)004:1108: dkyil 'khor che chung gang ltar kyang sbyar chog pas
NK041(di)004:1110: gzhan du gnas khang yangs pa dang /
NK041(di)004:1111: sbyin bdag 'byor ba can gyis dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs pa'i cha gsum nang ma dang /
NK041(di)004:1112: pho brang bar mas sgo brgyad /
NK041(di)004:1113: phyi ma cha gsum gyi nang ma khyams dang /
NK041(di)004:1114: phyi ma gnyis la sgo bton te /
NK041(di)004:1115: phyi rol du de'i sgo tshad dang mnyam pa'i rta
NK041(di)004:1116: bab sogs byas nas rwa rtse nas phyi rol gyi
NK041(di)004:1117: khor yug bskor chog pa sogs lag len du bya
NK041(di)004:1118: sla zhing mdzes pa zhig 'byung ngo //
NK041(di)004:1119: 'on kyang dkyil 'khor chung ngu'i tshe cha gsum bar
NK041(di)004:1120: ma la sgo brgyad brtsegs bya dka' ba'i gnas su
NK041(di)004:1122: dong sprugs kyi pad+ma brgya'i 'god lugs ni /
NK041(di)004:1124: mu khyud drug skor rim pa lnga //
NK041(di)004:1125: bzhi brgyad bcu drug sum cu gnyis //
NK041(di)004:1126: tha ma bzhi bcur 'gyur ba yin //
NK041(di)004:1128: 'dir sgo rkyang 'gram log dang bral ba dang /
NK041(di)004:1129: rta bab cha mi mnyam par mdzad pa sogs ni brtag pa'i gnas te /
NK041(di)004:1130: rgyu mtshan blos bslang rnam bzhag tu bshad grub bo //
NK041(di)004:1131: da ni rta bab bzhi ma las 'phros pa'i dkyil 'khor so so'i gdab tshul ni /
NK041(di)004:1132: gter ma phal che bar lha snam mi dgos pa'i
NK041(di)004:1133: khyams spangs te zhi ba bsdus pa dang 'dra bar
NK041(di)004:1134: byas mod / 'on kyang 'joms byed kyi dkyil chog
NK041(di)004:1135: tu khyams bshad pas gzhan ma rnams la'ang yod med
NK041(di)004:1136: 'dam khar byas na rung ngam snyam mo //
NK041(di)004:1138: 'dir rta bab bzhi mar bshad pa ni /
NK041(di)004:1139: slob dpon gyi thig chog las /
NK041(di)004:1140: cha gcig cha bzhir rta bab ste //
NK041(di)004:1142: bdun pa'i cha phran bzhi ru gdab //
NK041(di)004:1144: 'on kyang zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK041(di)004:1145: de nas sa thig rim pa bzhin //
NK041(di)004:1146: dgu dgu'i bdag nyid bco brgyad du //
NK041(di)004:1147: cha yi rnam pa la sogs bgo //
NK041(di)004:1149: zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi sgrub thabs las kyang /
NK041(di)004:1150: rnam thar bzhi yi sgo khyud la //
NK041(di)004:1151: rnam thar brgyad kyi rta bab ldan //
NK041(di)004:1152: zhes brgyad mar gsungs pa'ang yod pas mtha' gcig tu ma nges so //
NK041(di)004:1153: phyi rol gyi khor yug kyang /
NK041(di)004:1155: dang po 'jig rten phyogs skyong la gnyis pa rdo
NK041(di)004:1156: rje'i ra ba ste gsum pa me ri rab tu
NK041(di)004:1157: bri zhes dang / dkyil 'khor bya ba'i rim pa las /
NK041(di)004:1158: phyogs skyong snam bu dkar po'i sna tshogs pad+ma zhes 'byung bas /
NK041(di)004:1159: 'dir sgyu 'phrul zhi ba ltar pad+ma byas mod /
NK041(di)004:1161: pad ra'i tshab tu phyogs skyong snam bu bya ba'am /
NK041(di)004:1162: rnam pa gcig tu na pad+ma'i lte ba'i kha khyer
NK041(di)004:1163: la phyogs skyong bkod kyang mi 'gal lam snyam mo
NK041(di)004:1164: // 'di nang gi pho brang dgu la rta bab byed pa ni mi rigs te /
NK041(di)004:1166: dbus kyi pho brang dgu po la //
NK041(di)004:1167: sgo rgyan rta bab med pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1169: khro bo'i skabs 'dir nang sgo rnams la rta bab mi byed pa dang /
NK041(di)004:1171: dang po ni rtsa rgyud kyi le'u brgyad par /
NK041(di)004:1172: de las dkyil 'khor chen po dgu //
NK041(di)004:1173: kun kyang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NK041(di)004:1174: gru chad bar khyams sgo bzhir ldan //
NK041(di)004:1175: de dag phyi khyams sgo rnams dang //
NK041(di)004:1176: sgo rgyan lcags ri ldan pa ni //
NK041(di)004:1177: tshon sna lnga yis legs par bris //
NK041(di)004:1178: zhes nang sgo la sgo rgyan las ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)004:1180: bskyed rdzogs 'bring po'i mngon rtogs las /
NK041(di)004:1182: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i brdar rta bab bzhi pa /
NK041(di)004:1184: des na 'dir bla ma'i phyag len du rta bab med pa'i phyogs mdzad do //
NK041(di)004:1185: rta bab kyi snam bu ni brgyad ma dang /
NK041(di)004:1186: bzhi pa mchod rten gyi dbyibs /
NK041(di)004:1187: bzhi ma spyi 'gre ltar gsum las /
NK041(di)004:1189: sgrub thabs rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba sgom khog chen mor grags pa las /
NK041(di)004:1190: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang ldan pas rta bab brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK041(di)004:1191: zhes gsungs pa ltar deng sang phyag len 'di mdzad do //
NK041(di)004:1194: rta babs mdzes pa'i mchod rten 'dra //
NK041(di)004:1196: pu shu bang rim brtsegs la mchod rten 'dra bar
NK041(di)004:1197: gsungs pa ltar 'dra ba yin pas dgos pa'i nges
NK041(di)004:1198: pa med do // yang rnam pa gcig tu na /
NK041(di)004:1199: gsang rdzogs las rta bab mchod rten gzugs su bshad pa'i lhan pa shor ba snyam mo //
NK041(di)004:1200: gsum pa ni rtsa rgyud las /
NK041(di)004:1201: ba su ta'am rgyus pa yis //
NK041(di)004:1202: thig ni bcu drug gdab par bya //
NK041(di)004:1203: zhes cha chen bcu drug tu gsungs pas snam phran
NK041(di)004:1204: bzhir 'gyur ba'i phyir 'dir yang zhi ba ltar bzhi
NK041(di)004:1205: ma dang brgyad ma 'dam kha gsungs pa 'dra'o //
NK041(di)004:1206: phur pa spu gri'i gru chad la thod brtsigs byed
NK041(di)004:1207: pa ni blos bslangs kyi dus su gzhal yas khang
NK041(di)004:1208: phyi ma las mtho bar bzhed pas mu khyud kyi
NK041(di)004:1209: thod phreng lta bu ma yin zhing /
NK041(di)004:1210: 'di'i sgo la sgo khyud sogs med pas bri ba'i
NK041(di)004:1211: dus su sgo'i thad du rtsig pa gcod mi dgos
NK041(di)004:1212: te / sgo gong gi rtsig pa yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK041(di)004:1213: bka' brgyad gsang rdzogs la'ang pho brang nang ma'i thig 'di dang 'dra ba las /
NK041(di)004:1214: de'i steng gdung bzhi bsnol ba'i ling tshe dgur 'khor
NK041(di)004:1215: lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar zla gam logs sgo can
NK041(di)004:1216: re mdzad do // zla gam 'di la lte bar
NK041(di)004:1217: zlum po nyid gshags chog pas thig mi dgos kyang
NK041(di)004:1218: re mdzad do // / gzhan du dbang gi thab khung lta bu zla gam dgos pa'i rigs la /
NK041(di)004:1220: tshangs zur spyi ltar btab pa'i rjes //
NK041(di)004:1221: dbus nas shar du bskor thig gi //
NK041(di)004:1222: bzhi cha 'phags par srad bu bzung //
NK041(di)004:1223: shar gyi g.yas g.yon zur thig bar //
NK041(di)004:1224: bskor ba'i mdun logs bcad pas 'byung //
NK041(di)004:1225: pad 'dab brgyad ni tshangs zur rnams //
NK041(di)004:1226: thams cad phyed mar bcad pas grub //
NK041(di)004:1227: rtsibs bzhir tshangs rtse bzhi po sbrel //
NK041(di)004:1228: rtsibs brgyad de steng zur rtse'ang sbrel //
NK041(di)004:1229: rtsibs bcu tshangs nas tshangs gcig par //
NK041(di)004:1230: dum bu phyed gsum gzhal ba yi //
NK041(di)004:1231: phyed gnyis dor ba'i cha gcig pos //
NK041(di)004:1232: lho dang byang gi tshangs thig nas //
NK041(di)004:1233: shar nub gnyis kyi tshangs thig bar //
NK041(di)004:1234: gnyis re gzhal bas sgang po brgyad //
NK041(di)004:1235: phyed bcad mtshan ma brgyad btab bo //
NK041(di)004:1236: de steng shar nub tshangs thig bcad //
NK041(di)004:1237: mtshan ma bcu po gsal bar btab //
NK041(di)004:1238: mtshan ma gnyis gnyis bar bzhag nas //
NK041(di)004:1239: srad bu brkyangs te rim par gdab //
NK041(di)004:1241: zhes pa rnams kyang zhar la 'phros pa ste /
NK041(di)004:1242: thig gi cho ga cung zad dkrol ba'o //
NK041(di)004:1243: gnyis pa tshon gyi bya ba la'ang bzhi ste /
NK041(di)004:1248: dang po la'ang 'byor pa rab 'bring tha gsum las /
NK041(di)004:1249: 'byor pa rab 'bring ba'i yon bdag 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i dbang du byas na /
NK041(di)004:1252: ser po pu sha r+aa ga'am gser /
NK041(di)004:1253: dmar po pad+ma r+aa ga'am bye ru /
NK041(di)004:1254: ljang gu mrgad dam g.yu las bya ste /
NK041(di)004:1256: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i rdzas //
NK041(di)004:1257: pu sha r+aa ga gser dang ni //
NK041(di)004:1259: in+d+ra n+ai la tshon du sbyar //
NK041(di)004:1263: pu sha r+aa ga bye ru zangs //
NK041(di)004:1264: mrgad ta las bya ste dgye //
NK041(di)004:1266: 'byor pa 'bring rgyal phran rnams kyis 'bru lnga dang sman lnga gang rung rang mdog gam /
NK041(di)004:1267: tshon rtsis kha dog bsgyur ba las bya ste /
NK041(di)004:1269: mi yi dbang pos so nam 'bras //
NK041(di)004:1270: bra ro ram bu des dmar dang //
NK041(di)004:1271: ljang gu sran ma la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:1274: 'bras dang s+aa lu la sogs pa //
NK041(di)004:1275: kha dog bsgyur ba de bzhin no //
NK041(di)004:1278: 'byor pa chung ba 'bangs phal pas ni /
NK041(di)004:1279: bkra shis pa'i sa phyogs nas byung ba'i sa tshon
NK041(di)004:1280: rang mdog gam kha dog bsgyur ba la bya ste
NK041(di)004:1283: 'byung khung lnga yis bri bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1286: rdo thal ba bla sdong ros dang //
NK041(di)004:1287: rgya skyegs dmar po bya ba dang //
NK041(di)004:1288: ram las byas dang 'bru bsregs pa //
NK041(di)004:1289: thal ba'i rdul tshon dag tu bshad //
NK041(di)004:1291: de dag ni phyi'i tshon no //
NK041(di)004:1292: nang du drag po'i tshon ni /
NK041(di)004:1294: dur khrod thal chen sdong ros dang //
NK041(di)004:1295: de yi so phag dur sa dang //
NK041(di)004:1296: sol bas bri ba khro bo'o //
NK041(di)004:1298: khro dkyil bzhengs pa'i tshon lnga la thal chen cung zad re bsre ba phyag len no //
NK041(di)004:1300: zhi khro thun mong la 'bras bu chen po lnga /
NK041(di)004:1302: yum mtshan ldan gyi pad+ma rak+tasa bri bar bshad de /
NK041(di)004:1304: ri mo gcig pa zhes bya ba //
NK041(di)004:1305: de dag thams cad ri mo gcig /
NK041(di)004:1306: chags pa'i rak+ta byang chub sems //
NK041(di)004:1307: dkyil 'khor kun gyi tshon rtsir bshad //
NK041(di)004:1309: da ni thun mong du nye bar mkho ba rdul
NK041(di)004:1310: tshon bsgyur ba'i lag len cung zad bri bar bya
NK041(di)004:1311: ste / kun gyi gzhi ma dkar po ni //
NK041(di)004:1312: r+aa ga rab la cong zhi tha //
NK041(di)004:1313: gtun brdung chu bsil gyis btul te //
NK041(di)004:1314: dar gyi tshags mas 'tshag pa gces //
NK041(di)004:1315: dmar rtsi zhos byug nyi 'od la //
NK041(di)004:1316: bsregs nas ma skam tsam gyi dus //
NK041(di)004:1317: sa bsres rang mdog ma thon bar //
NK041(di)004:1318: legs par mnyed pas dmar legs 'byung //
NK041(di)004:1319: de brlan ma bral rdo zho ni //
NK041(di)004:1320: btul po dang sbyar legs 'phur na //
NK041(di)004:1321: mthing gi mdangs 'od zil gyis gnon //
NK041(di)004:1322: ram btul de dang sa sbyar nas //
NK041(di)004:1324: ba mos ma reg ston dus kyi //
NK041(di)004:1325: spang rgyan sked gtub byas pa yis //
NK041(di)004:1326: rtse mo'i cha rnams zhib mor brdung //
NK041(di)004:1327: de dang sa bsres slar brdungs nas //
NK041(di)004:1328: nyi ma'i 'od du mnye zhing bsreg /
NK041(di)004:1329: lan gnyis lan gsum sgyur ba na //
NK041(di)004:1330: kha dog sngon po phyi bzhin legs //
NK041(di)004:1331: de la rdo zho btul po ni //
NK041(di)004:1332: zhib btags cung zad btab byas nas //
NK041(di)004:1333: brdung zhing mnye nas nyi 'od la //
NK041(di)004:1334: bsregs pas kha dog ljang gu 'byung //
NK041(di)004:1335: gro ljang gzhon nu ha lo'i 'dab //
NK041(di)004:1336: sran ma gzhon nu sogs brdungs nas //
NK041(di)004:1337: sa bsregs mnye zhing nyi mar skam //
NK041(di)004:1339: yung ba zhib btags zhor sbyar nas //
NK041(di)004:1340: sa dkar bsres la grib skam bya //
NK041(di)004:1341: btso ma gser gyi kha dog 'dzin //
NK041(di)004:1342: yang na zho dang ma sbyar kyang //
NK041(di)004:1343: sngar bzhin byas pas ser po 'ong //
NK041(di)004:1344: de nyid rdo zho'am bul tog dang //
NK041(di)004:1345: sbyar bas ngur smrig bzang por 'byung //
NK041(di)004:1346: spang ma'i phye dang snum sbyar nas //
NK041(di)004:1347: mer bsregs mig sman mdog dang mtshungs //
NK041(di)004:1348: zhes mdo tsam smras pa ste /
NK041(di)004:1349: zhib par mkhas pa'i lag len la lta ba gces so //
NK041(di)004:1351: gzhi'i tshon gyi tshad 'phang la re kh+aa'i phyed phyed
NK041(di)004:1352: de re kh+aa'i 'phang du ni cha phran gyi lnga
NK041(di)004:1355: khri'u ris med par bkye ba'o //
NK041(di)004:1357: tshon rnams snod gtsang mar blugs pa la rigs lnga'i
NK041(di)004:1358: sa bon bris pa phyogs ma 'khrul bar bkod la
NK041(di)004:1360: rgyal ba rigs chung dang bcas pa lnga tshan lngar
NK041(di)004:1361: gsal ba rjes chags kyis zhu ba las don ye
NK041(di)004:1362: shes lnga mtshon pa'i rtags rat+na lngar gyur par bsam
NK041(di)004:1364: snod blugs rim 'dres dag byas la //
NK041(di)004:1365: h'u sogs yig 'bru gcig kyang lngar //
NK041(di)004:1366: kha dog rjes su mthun byas la //
NK041(di)004:1367: yongs gyur nyi shu rtsa lnga'i lha //
NK041(di)004:1368: thabs dang shes rab ldan par bsgom //
NK041(di)004:1371: de la rigs kyi yi ge bkod //
NK041(di)004:1373: lha rnams 'od zhu tshon la thim //
NK041(di)004:1374: rat+na lnga ru gyur par bsam //
NK041(di)004:1377: yi ge 'bru lngas byin brlabs pa //
NK041(di)004:1378: phyag mtshan rigs lnga yab yum gyur //
NK041(di)004:1379: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK041(di)004:1381: thog mar slob dpon shar du zhal phyogs pas tshon
NK041(di)004:1382: la bkod pa'i yig 'bru rnams mtheb srin gyis blangs
NK041(di)004:1383: te / khung bu dgang ba ni /
NK041(di)004:1385: tshon ni nang nas dgye bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1386: phyi rol nas ni tshon mi dgye //
NK041(di)004:1388: de la lag pa la dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod de /
NK041(di)004:1389: tshon pra brtags pa'i don du g.yon pa'i khu tshur
NK041(di)004:1390: gyis dbang ldan nas brtsams la mdzub gang ba'i pany+tsa
NK041(di)004:1393: tshon re sgo yi nyi shu cha //
NK041(di)004:1394: dpangs ni mda' tsam bri bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1397: byang shar mtshams kyi re kh+aa la //
NK041(di)004:1398: sa bon pra ni brtags par bya //
NK041(di)004:1399: nag po dkar po ser po dmar //
NK041(di)004:1400: ljang gu rnam lnga manya ma par sbyar //
NK041(di)004:1401: mdzub gang du ni bri bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1403: de rjes slob ma rnams kyis kyang /
NK041(di)004:1404: sor mor 'bru lnga bkod de ci bder bri'o //
NK041(di)004:1405: de yang rdul tshon kha dog lnga so sor phye ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK041(di)004:1407: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK041(di)004:1408: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab kyang //
NK041(di)004:1409: rang gi rnam rtog bsgribs byas nas //
NK041(di)004:1410: ye shes lnga yi don ma mthong //
NK041(di)004:1411: de ltar rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK041(di)004:1412: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)004:1413: dkar dang dmar dang ser ba dang //
NK041(di)004:1414: ljang gu la sogs nag po bstan //
NK041(di)004:1418: ji ltar dgye ba'i rim pa ni //
NK041(di)004:1420: tshon dgye ba'i khyad par gyi cho ga rnams zhib
NK041(di)004:1421: mor ston pa ste gzhung bklags pas 'grub pa'i phyir
NK041(di)004:1422: ma bkrol lo // tshon dgye ba grub nas mtshan ma dgod pa ni /
NK041(di)004:1423: de ltar dkyil 'khor so so yi //
NK041(di)004:1426: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK041(di)004:1427: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK041(di)004:1428: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK041(di)004:1431: dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum dag tu //
NK041(di)004:1432: gzhung nyid kyis ni gsal bar gsungs //
NK041(di)004:1433: yan lag gzugs su snying po 'di //
NK041(di)004:1434: nyi zla pad+ma'i rim bzhugs pa //
NK041(di)004:1435: dkyil 'khor sku yi mtshan nyid yin //
NK041(di)004:1436: phyag rgya gsal bkod thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK041(di)004:1437: sku'am yang na h'u mum bri //
NK041(di)004:1438: mchog dang 'bring pos phye ba ni //
NK041(di)004:1439: dkyil 'khor gsum du phye bar bya //
NK041(di)004:1441: mdor na so so'i sogs te /
NK041(di)004:1442: tshon rtsi srab na dbul por 'gyur /
NK041(di)004:1444: tshon thal shor na nad 'byung ba sogs gsungs shing /
NK041(di)004:1445: khyad par du tshon pra brtag pa'i tshe /
NK041(di)004:1446: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dzas /
NK041(di)004:1447: re kh+aa dma' bas mi 'grub cing //
NK041(di)004:1448: yon pos gdung ba skyed par byed //
NK041(di)004:1449: chad pas slob dpon slob ma la //
NK041(di)004:1451: lhag chad las ni nad 'byung zhing //
NK041(di)004:1453: zhes gsungs pas bag yod pas bri'o //
NK041(di)004:1454: gang zhig blo gros sogs te /
NK041(di)004:1455: thig tshon gyi bya ba rnams ji bzhin ma grub pas skyon du gyur na /
NK041(di)004:1456: drag po'i sbyin sreg dang sngags bzla ba sogs so so'i snying po'i cho ga dang /
NK041(di)004:1457: gtso bor de kho na nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK041(di)004:1458: gyis skyon thams cad sel ba yin pas 'bad de
NK041(di)004:1460: de dag kyang zhib par dkyil chog so so dang /
NK041(di)004:1461: bla ma'i phyag len mthong ba goms pa la rag
NK041(di)004:1462: las pas bla ma'i man ngag thob pa la brtson
NK041(di)004:1463: par bya yi / 'dir brjod pa ni mdo tsam mo //
NK041(di)004:1464: de ltar gter chen bla ma chos kyi rje'i //
NK041(di)004:1465: zhabs rdul spyi bo'i pad+mora rtag bzhugs shing //
NK041(di)004:1466: snying dbus do rar mtshan dpe'i gar rtsen pa'i //
NK041(di)004:1467: skal bzang sngags btsun d+harma sh+r+ais sbyar //
